        [
          "Staff Generated History"
        ],
        [
          "Your sire embraced you and stuck around for a year in disregard of normal embracement traditions of Clan Gangrel.  He specifically picked you to fulfill a role that was missing in the local Camarilla, that of the Computer Nerd.  The local court did not have a young embrace familiar with modern technology and your sire in an attempt to fill that need and enhance Clan Gangrels standing with the Court specifically sought you out.  He found you working in the back room of \"Jim's Computer Repair\" where you had been keeping your boss's, Jim, business afloat all by yourself for over a year.  You were self taught but a natural.  As your sire brought you into the world of the Camarilla you realized more and more what a bad choice this was, especially as a Gangrel. Very few of your clan will even hold still to use a phone let alone have any knowledge of Data mining or what benefits running VPN for external clients offers.  You have made your way slowly and with little success so far but LA may be a new start, as well you have heard rumours that not all of your clan in the city are Luddites."
